                    h2 Profile of the study program

                .decptext.text-start
                    p.lead The digital transformation of the last decades has revolutionized the way people relate to information. Today's reality focuses on information as the competitive and differentiating engine of organizations. The volume, complexity, structuring and mechanisms for providing information today require a much more demanding profile from the marketing professional, with regard to the tools he has to work in a more analytical way and with a very demanding time-to-market.
                    p.lead The Post-Graduation in Digital Marketing aims to create assets with a 360° vision focused on the customer and the definition of differentiating local and global strategies, with the potential to generate competitive advantages for organizations, integrating knowledge and technological skills to streamline and optimize data-driven decision-making.
        section#diplomados.mt-5
